hopobject.body: Languages urangan marina pharmacy urangan qld James Pattinson was broken physically by England - and by his own team-mates who failed to bat long enough to give him time to recover at Lord’s. Here in a nutshell, or plaster-cast, was the explanation for why countries no longer enforce the follow-on: England batted for more than 100 overs in both innings, Australia for less than four hours in their first, so the overload resulted in a stress fracture of Pattinson’s back that might also keep him out of this winter’s series.
